title: Gruntruck - Inside Yours [Japanese Release].zip
description:
Gruntruck "Inside Yours"
Apollon International, 1992

This is the Apollon International (Japan) version of the "Inside Yours" title as released on Roadrunner Records. "Inside Yours" was originally released on the eMpTy/Musical Tragedies label in 1991.

Booklet scan included with lyrics in English and Japanese.

Gruntruck was a hard rock band from Seattle, active from 1989 to 2002.
